A warm, soft-lit Studio Ghibli style illustration of two young twin boys with matching backpacks standing at the edge of a quiet suburban street in the pale blue light of early dawn, a yellow school bus approaching in the distance with its headlights glowing warmly, cherry blossom petals drifting through the cool morning air, the boys casting long shadows behind them as the first golden rays of sunrise peek over rooftops, their bicycles leaning forgotten against a garden fence nearby, capturing the bittersweet feeling of childhood transitions and early morning new beginnings.
